      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does a new boiler installation cost in Liverpool?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A like-for-like combi boiler installation in Liverpool starts from £1,800 fully fitted. System boilers start from £2,200 and regular boilers from £2,500. All prices include the boiler, installation, controls, Benchmark certificate and Gas Safe certificate. Call 0151 558 0334 for a free fixed-price survey." } },
